# arvo-strategy

Strategy markers and the type-only container-projection traits.
`Hot`, `Warm`, `Cold`, `Precise` ZSTs identify the precision /
throughput tradeoff. `UContainerFor<N>` and `IContainerFor<N>` const
traits project a strategy + bit-width to the bare primitive container
that holds it. `#![no_std]`, no alloc.
